<%= content_for :page_title, raw("PE courses for 2021&thinsp;–&thinsp;2022") %>
<%= content_for :before_content, render_breadcrumbs("allocations_closed") %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">PE courses for 2021&thinsp;–&thinsp;2022</h1>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      You can no longer request fee-funded PE for 2021 - 2022. The request window closed on 10 July.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      Your requests are set out below. In September, we’ll tell you if they’ve been approved and,
      if so, how many places have been allocated for each organisation.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      Also included are current courses that were not requested for 2021&thinsp;–&thinsp;2022.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      For now, if you have any questions contact <%= bat_contact_mail_to %>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Courses for 2021&thinsp;–&thinsp;2022
    </h2>

    <%= render partial: "providers/allocations/allocation_report_closed_state", locals: {
               allocations: @allocations_view.requested_allocations_statuses,
               request_type: "repeat"} %>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Courses not running in 2021&thinsp;–&thinsp;2022
    </h2>

    <%= render partial: "providers/allocations/allocation_report_closed_state", locals: {
               allocations: @allocations_view.not_requested_allocations_statuses,
               request_type: "repeat"} %>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      You did not request fee-funded PE for 2021&thinsp;–&thinsp;2022.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      Your organisation, and any organisations you’re the accredited body for,
      will not be offering this course - even if it’s being offered in 2020&thinsp;–&thinsp;2021.
      You must have permission to run this course in 2021&thinsp;–&thinsp;2022.
    </p>

    <p class="govuk-body">
      If you have any questions, contact <%= bat_contact_mail_to %>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">
      Tell us what you think about this process
    </h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      <%= link_to "Take part in our brief survey to help us improve Publish",
                  "https://forms.gle/4EuNG8XGm3AqavRU9",
                  class: "govuk-link govuk-!-font-weight-bold",
                  target: "_blank" %>

  </div>
</div>
